To find activities, navigate to the "Activities" tab in the navbar. Here, you will be presented with
a calendar view of all activities. You can navigate between months by clicking the arrows on the top.

<%= image_tag "help/calendar.png", alt: "Profile Picture", class: "img-fluid" %>

You may also wish to view the activities in a list view. To do this, click the "List" button on the
"Activities" page. You can then click on an activity to view more details about it.

